snippet.title: Zombie Army 4: Dead War trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019
snippet.description: Rebellion's next Zombie Army game revealed, and yes it has Zombie Hitler in it. Though details are scarce, you can read everything we know about it here: https://www.pcgamer.com/zombie-army-4-dead-war-is-a-co-op-battle-against-zombie-hitlers-hordes/
